Environment Setup:

1) Installed Docker Containers
        
        1. MySql
        2. Phpmyadmin 
        3. Wordpress 

        i. Angular Material:=>  ng add @angular/material --save

        ii. sudo ngBootstrap (Ensure file permission):=>  sudo ng add @ng-bootstrap/schematics --save

        iii. change owner:=>   chown -R dane:dane fileName

        iv. change permissions :=> chmod -R 777 fileName

        v. npm install wp-api-angular --save

        vi. npm install -g typings

2) Installed Angular and Ionic 
        1. Create Ionic App 
        2. Install Material Design
        3. Install WP-api-angular 
        4. Install typings 
        
3) Configured Wordpress
        1. Create Theme
        2. Configure BootStrap
        3. Install JWT Authentication Plugin
        4. Install Redis Plugin

4) Added Github Version Control : 
        1. To remove commits from cache => git rm --cached ./* -r

5) Configured Gulp task runner

6) Setup Production Server
        1. ** Nginx and php-FPM **
        2. ** Install Redis container **


7) Create website Frontend pages
        1. Ionic Home page 
        2. Wordpress Front-page 


8) Create Scrollable label Component 
        1. Ionic Scrollpane 
        2. Wordpress blog page

9) View Single page Component
        1. Ionic Single view item Component
        2. Wordpress Single page

10) User Accounts and Authentication

        1. Signup and Login 
        2. Add Display Image 





